---
title: Bacon and Aubergine Parmigiana Style Pasta with Mozzarella and Rocket Salad
description: Parmigiana is an Italian dish made with roasted or fried aubergine layered with tomato sauce and cheese before being baked. Our Bacon and Aubergine Parmigiana Style Pasta adds penne and a fresh rocket salad on the side to make a filling meal.
